org.geppetto.model.datasources

Interface RunnableQuery

  • All Known Implementing Classes:
    RunnableQueryImpl

    public interface RunnableQuery
    A representation of the model object 'Runnable Query'.

    The following features are supported:

    • Target Variable Path
    • Query Path
    • Boolean Operator
    See Also:
